						<div class="postbody">Super Mario Bros. Pseudo code:<br /><br /><div class="codetitle"><b>Code:</b></div><div class="codecontent">if ( (PseudoRandom&#91;0&#93; &amp; 2) ^ (PseudoRandom&#91;1&#93; &amp; 2) ) == 0<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; clc<br />else<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; sec<br />endif<br /><br />for x = 0 to 6 {<br />&nbsp; ror PseudoRandom&#91; x &#93;<br />}<br /></div><br /><br />I should add: PseudoRandom[0] is initialized with $A5.<br /><br />Also you could say:<br /><br /><div class="codetitle"><b>Code:</b></div><div class="codecontent">c = ( (PseudoRandom&#91;0&#93; &amp; 2) ^ (PseudoRandom&#91;1&#93; &amp; 2) )<br /><br />for x = 0 to 6 {<br />&nbsp; ror PseudoRandom&#91; x &#93;<br />}<br /></div></div>

					
