						<div class="postbody"><a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Linear_feedback_shift_register#Galois_LFSRs" class="postlink">Galois</a> and <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Linear_feedback_shift_register#Fibonacci_LFSRs" class="postlink">Fibonacci</a> are just two &quot;opposite&quot; ways to implement a particular LFSR (with Galois being simpler in software).</div>

